<article
  class="flex flex-col items-center gap-8 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300 md:flex-row m-5"
>
  <div
    class="[&>p]:mb-4 [&>p>strong]:text-yellow-400 text-bold dark:[&>p>strong]:text-yellow-400 [&>p>strong]:font-normal [&>p>strong]:font-mono text-pretty order-2 md:order-1"
  >
    <p>
      Hi there! I'm a dedicated Software Engineer with over 5 years of
      experience. I started coding in high school and deepened my skills through
      a two-year
      <strong>Web development</strong> course. This path led me to Ireland, where
      I completed a degree in <strong>Computer Science</strong>, paving the way
      for a variety of opportunities in Software Engineering.
    </p>

    <p>
      At present, I work as a <strong>Frontend Engineer</strong> at a <strong
