      visualisations to enhance security solutions. With over four years of
      experience in <strong>JavaScript, TypeScript, and React</strong>, I excel
      in designing and implementing complex UI components.
    </p>

    <p>
      Beyond work, I'm passionate about continuous learning and growth, actively
      seeking new challenges to expand my skills in evolving technologies. My
      goal is to continue to contribute meaningfully to Software Engineering in
      a collaborative and innovative environment.
    </p>
